23:05.566 --> 23:10.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STUDENT: People, if they don't
know how to analyze it, will
just say, oh, wow, that's

23:11.233 --> 23:13.366 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
