23:13.366 --> 23:15.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: Fred Coddon
(ph) looks at the choice of
words used in a story about

23:15.566 --> 23:18.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
