and have my own opinion.

24:12.266 --> 24:14.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
NIAMH O'CONNELL: They soak
up everything around them.

24:14.833 --> 24:19.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think it's important for
kids to be able to control the
interpretations that they hear

24:21.800 --> 24:24.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
