showed they were easily duped

25:00.533 --> 25:02.500 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
online.

25:02.500 --> 25:06.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Researchers found, overall,
young people's ability to
reason about the information on

25:07.900 --> 25:11.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the Internet can be summed
up in one word: bleak.

25:13.033 --> 25:14.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
