the audience a lesson or
to talk about technology.

39:53.733 --> 39:57.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
We just wanted to tell
this story and hopefully
illuminate something
about the world in doing

39:57.500 --> 39:59.600 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
this.

39:59.600 --> 40:01.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHAEL GREIF, Director: Yes,
and like in all the -- in all
great theater writing, those

40:01.200 --> 40:03.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
