through that story.

40:03.933 --> 40:08.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And those things become
a part of Evan's story
and a part of his world.

40:10.933 --> 40:13.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Director Michael
Greif previously staged two
Pulitzer Prize-winning musicals,

40:13.933 --> 40:18.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
