can tell difficult stories.

40:24.900 --> 40:26.900 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MICHAEL GREIF: Yes, certainly.

40:26.900 --> 40:29.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
