different kinds of musicals.

40:29.633 --> 40:34.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And the musicals I was always
particularly drawn to were --
"Man of La Mancha," I think

40:34.233 --> 40:36.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
