40:43.633 --> 40:47.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
musicals that really do say
something real and authentic
about "The Times" that they

40:47.966 --> 40:50.533 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
were made in.

40:50.533 --> 40:53.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: "Dear Evan
Hansen" has certainly
struck a chord with
audiences, and many have

40:53.600 --> 40:58.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
