41:14.833 --> 41:18.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
NARRATOR: "The 'Dear
Evan Hansen' soundtrack
has saved my life."

41:18.200 --> 41:22.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NARRATOR: "Last night, I
found out my dear high school
friend had taken his own life

41:22.766 --> 41:24.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
